<view class='saying' hidden>
  <view animation='{{adt}}' wx:if='{{code>0}}' style='opacity:0;margin:50rpx 0 0 60rpx;position: relative;'>
    <span></span>
    <view bindtap="aa">Hi，<open-data type="userNickName"></open-data></view>
  </view>
  <view animation='{{adt}}' wx:if='{{code>1}}' style='opacity:0;margin:50rpx 0 0 60rpx;position: relative;'>
    <span></span>
    <view>马上要开始学习了 感觉怎么样呀！</view>
  </view>
  <view animation='{{adt}}' wx:if='{{code>2}}' style='opacity:0;margin:50rpx 0 0 60rpx;position: relative;'>
    <span></span>
    <view><text>刚开始学不会没关系，\n坚持学习会有收获的！</text></view>
  </view>
  <view animation='{{adt}}' wx:if='{{code>3}}' style='opacity:0;margin:50rpx 0 0 60rpx;position: relative;'>
    <span></span>
    <view>加油，看好你哟！</view>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="index">
  <view class="navbar" style="height:{{navbarH}}px;">
    <view style="border:2px solid;border-radius:50%;width:32px;height:32px;position:absolute;left:10px;bottom:5px;"></view>
  </view>
  <view class='body'>
    <view class="date">
        <text>March，22nd，2019</text>
    </view>
    <view class="title">
      <text>The harder you work,The luckier you will be.Shu</text>
    </view>
    <view class="type">
      <span>R</span><text>eal-time news</text>
    </view>
    <view class="img">
      <image src="../../static/img/neza.jpg"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="audio">
      <view class="iconfont {{playflag ? 'icon-bofang' : 'icon-pause'}}" bindtap='play'></view>
      
      <text>00:05</text>
      <view class="slider" bindtouchmove="move" bindtap="tap" bindtouchend="end">
        <view style="width:{{sliderW}}"><p catchtouchstart="start"><span></span></p></view>
      </view>
      <text>05:05</text>
    </view>
    <view class='article'>
      <view class="english">Scientists <span bindtap='findWord'>revealed<icon></icon></span> an asteroid dubbed by some as a "city killer" came closer to the Earth than the moon this week.</view>
      <view class="chinese" hidden='{{translate}}'>科学家透露本周有一颗被科学家戏称为“城市杀手”的小行星距离地球比月球还近。</view>
      <view class="english">Scientists revealed an asteroid dubbed by some as a "city killer" came closer to the Earth than the moon this week.</view>
      <view class="chinese" hidden='{{translate}}'>科学家透露本周有一颗被科学家戏称为“城市杀手”的小行星距离地球比月球还近。</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="footer">
    <view>
      <image></image>
      <text>已收藏</text>
    </view>
    <view bindtap='translate'>
      <image></image>
      <text>{{translate ? '翻译' : '原文'}}</text>
    </view>
    <view bindtap="toStudy">
      <image></image>
      <text>下一项</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

